com.bandyer.core_av.audiosession

Enum AudioOutputDeviceType


  • public enum AudioOutputDeviceType

    Class which represents an audio hardware output device.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      BLUETOOTH
      Any bluetooth device capable of playing audio.
      EARPIECE
      Earpiece, available in phones.
      NONE
      Representation of no available outputs or muted status.
      SPEAKER_PHONE
      Device loudspeaker.
      WIRED_HEADSET
      Wired headset with or without mic.
